<MethodEndpoint
  method={"get"}
  path={"/domain_applications/{id}"}
  context={"endpoint"}
>
  
</MethodEndpoint>



Retrieves the details of a domain application that has been previously
created. Use the unique ID that was returned from your previous
request to identify the specific domain application.

#### Permissions
The API token must include the following scopes: _Voice_.
